1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,876
Here is one useful thing to watch for.

2
00:00:02,826 --> 00:00:05,947
Do not press hard or click many times.

3
00:00:05,947 --> 00:00:09,171
A light, single click is all it takes.

4
00:00:09,171 --> 00:00:13,831
If it happens, pause, reset, and try again calmly.

